CPSC-6820 Deliverable #3
Team: Happy Pets
Teammates: Sriram Vishnubhotla, Logan Swoyer
Project: Automatic Pet Feeder
Project Repository: https://github.com/hexlambda/CPSC-6820/
Project Overview: A pet feeding device with fine-grained scheduling settings and mobile connectivity.
Parts:
Piezoelectric Buzzer (PS1240P02BT)
Joystick (512)
Load Cell Amplifier (SEN-13879)
Microcontroller (MSP430FR5994)
OLED Display + Breakout board (SSD1306)
Proximity Sensor (VL6180V1NR)
WiFi Module + Breakout board (WINC1500)
